Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. This volume includes a homage to "The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter," a Japanese folk tale.
Title: SAILOR MOON SHORT STORIES, VOL. 2
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Wall Ros√© has been breached by the Titans leading Armin and Hange to double their efforts in discovering how the walls can be rebuilt.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 9
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: A new Turbo Duel hero named Yusei Fudo emerges from the outskirts of New Domino City and he will defeat any challenger thanks to his custom-built Duel Runner.
Title: YU-GI-OH 5D'S, VOL. 5
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato
Contributor: by Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato

Description: This series is about an incredibly positive young girl named Yotsuba. In this volume, she learns how to tie her shoes.
Title: YOTSUBA&!, VOL. 12
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: The Death Weapon Meister Academy face their enemies on multiple fronts as they race to find the evil god Asura before Noah and Medusa.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 17
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Alexia is shocked to discover that she is pregnant and becomes ostracized and dismissed by the Shadow Council as a result.
Title: SOULLESS, VOL. 3
Author: Gail Carriger and Rem

Description: This series adapts the plot from the role-playing video game, where Roxas joins the mysterious Organization XIII.
Title: KINGDOM HEARTS 358/2 DAYS, VOL. 1
Author: Shiro Amano

Description: In this latest volume, Naruto battles Tobi, who has brought the demonic Gedo statue to life.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 63
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, what happens when a human boy becomes a Titan?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 3
Author: Hajime Isayama
